name: JNoSQL
tagline: The JNoSQL is a framework whose has the goal to help Java developers to create Java EE applications with NoSQL, whereby they can make scalable application beyond enjoy the polyglot persistence.
body:
![JNoSQL Project](https://github.com/JNOSQL/diana-site/blob/master/images/duke-diana.png)

# JNoSQL


Eclipse JNoSQL is a flexible and extensible API to connect NoSQL databases. It brings an easy interface to support key-value, column family, document oriented and graph database
